              "name": "reply",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "Jarvis commands:\n/help — this message\n/status — system status\n/research <topic>\n/emails — inbox summary\n/image <prompt>\n/cyber — latest cyber threat brief\n/opportunities [org|date] — latest cyber opportunities brief (+ history/search)\n/energy [org|date] — latest energy intelligence brief (+ history/search)"
            }
          ]
        }
